text.tspan: Pursuing bachelor's degree in Civil Engineering from Cal State
Sarah is senior studying Civil Engineering at California State University. She
is the ﬁrst in her family to attend college and she is hoping to attend graduate school
Sarah is hoping to learn more about incorporating DAS data to help her in her
research on earthquake engineering. She isn't the most tech savvy so she wants to ﬁnd a
site that could easily displays data without coding.
One of her issues is that the available resources out are every diﬃcult to use
and understand for people who are not already familiar with it. Since she is not expert on
programming, its hard for her to use raw data that some of the existing websites have.
